Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,90,,Okay! Tighten the wires!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,90,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,90,,Move 'em! They're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey! Don't just put those anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,90,,Where... do I put?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,90,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,90,,Where the other cargo is!{More "Hora"? Hora hora. Hehe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,90,,Okay, move them over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,90,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no flying around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Don't just cut the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do something\N about this yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't yet decided how to manage your residency rights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so could you live here\N for the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is so inconvenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber close. Convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The invoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Invoice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They demand that you work to repay\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the damage you caused to the hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ridget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo's the one who chased off the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage of the hangar\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}is a separate matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But he just arrived here!\N He doesn't know anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not charge him for water or electricity during his stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and we will waive the freight\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}tax for this giant payload.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not simply a one-sided agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, are you sure\N you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your Yunboro's in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Move to where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the next load of cargo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and drop 'em off at the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber, take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say about flying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a Yunboro you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it understand people besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The transfer of command rights is permitted to the degree allowed by army regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boss! I got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hard at work I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's slacking off while the\N{\alpha&HFDF&}.{\r}metalhead does all the work.{ep3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That frickin' dolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We really oughta feed him to the fish—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be just taking a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot identify any logic\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}behind your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a way to focus my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised these people can\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}move about so much{to no avail!} in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no discipline here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are their instructors up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be conjectured that instructors\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}do not oversee the training of children here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how can they grow into \Nproductive members of society?{by not fansubbing}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Awaiting further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Completion of mission is currently hindered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Requesting permission to dispose of obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be mindful not to cause any damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I am standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing by? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Are you making something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making something you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange material.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideauze claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannot find on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got time for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my little brother will love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Little brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. His name's Bevel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really good at making stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "little brother" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Little brother" means a sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A younger sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Family"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A societal unit found in\N antiquated communities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,centered around a male-female\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}couple based on genetic relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of that custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Inefficient. Unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inefficient?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The place you come\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}from sounds really harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bevel wants to ask you about space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,About space?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's really interested in stars, and ships that can go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But his body's really frail, so he\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}can't exactly be out and about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Frail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got this... chest disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Galactic Alliance, weak individuals\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}are removed and disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Individuals incapable of combat\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}are considered unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unnecessary? And you\N just let that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand not the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Will talking to this person\N lead me to useful intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably talk\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to Dr. Ordum for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a doctor, but we call him\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the wise man of the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the most knowledgeable\N person on Gargantia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Dr. Ordum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Amy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Amy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! Oh, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a guest today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the famous Ledo, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I still have\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}work to do, so I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, I'll come pick you up,\N so wait for me downstairs later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like information from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but is that the voice of the machine that can understand our language?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost that technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can ask more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll answer to the best of my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of a way to return to the Galactic Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sadly, I don't know nearly\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}enough to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, most of the ancient\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}knowledge has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, that pertaining\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to interstellar travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all the knowledge\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}we have left about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt this is what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can ask another question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I request your explanation regarding\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the organization of this fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This fleet is inefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The chain of command and the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}training process are imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The behavior of the civilians is disorganized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I also cannot understand\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}why you protect the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that's what it looks\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}like to a visitor from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you have a very narrow\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}interpretation of what "efficiency" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should talk\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}with Bevel sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this person provide\N me with useful intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you to decide how useful it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So not even Doc knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.53,Default,,0,0,90,,Hey, Bevel! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,90,,Welcome back, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,90,,Is this Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,90,,He really {\i1}is{\i0} your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Bevel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.{Same thing re: choppiness, ellipses.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is Amy's "little brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo said he wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I request information from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Chamber talks\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}through this transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! It really {\i1}can{\i0} talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber{san}...{Quotation marks? Is he asking about what his name is? As in: He's called "Chamber"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an AI whose purpose\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}is to assist my pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even understand our language!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a hand. Can you fill in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{This was missing}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, look at this cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I gotta work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I was looking forward to this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to {\i1}what{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you cut that out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bevel, take care of Ledo for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to rush and fall over this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy!{BG}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry my sister's so busy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, are you really from space?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wondered what life in space would be like!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Galactic Alliance, our main task\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}is to defend against the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a Hideauze?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alien lifeforms that threaten humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you constantly fighting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The conflict has lasted since the founding of\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the Galactic Alliance up until the present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's totally different\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}from how we live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever get tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who tire, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you used to this place yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot comprehend the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}organization of Gargantia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to me the reason behind your\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}inefficient and unprofitable actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The fleet isn't an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We all just kind of gathered together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we fight, and\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}other times we help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the purpose of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we can live without worrying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your answer is questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of mankind is to subjugate the enemy, the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the steady progress of\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}mankind cannot be guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Galactic Alliance, people like you\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}would be weeded out{natural selection} immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeded out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, what'll happen to the Galactic Alliance once you defeat all the Hideauze?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be on standby,\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}awaiting my next orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what if no more come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will remain on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't standing by mean\N that you're "living on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear Joe took your Yunboro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've ruined your\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}hard-earned hero image.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Were my actions beneficial?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you got rid of the pirates for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, all I do\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}is oversee Chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just not used to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot determine which actions I am supposed to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposed to, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about leaving that\N soldier mentality behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. You could just let yourself—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Collect the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a weather phenomenon.\N It is not poisonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go collect the rain with your Yunboro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh water is precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some sailcloth over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread it out and collect the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I detect changes in your brainwaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if the army\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}made any progress in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At present, such thoughts are illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's {\i1}sooo{\i0} cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, I kinda\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's all alone in some\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}completely foreign place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. A cute guy\N like him will be just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! I know\N you're worried about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, you're soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna catch a cold like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my place to dry off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the squall was pretty intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I observed the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}phenomenon of concentrated rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it rain in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And sick people like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I'm not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to live on till now\N because someone needed you too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the lives of those who are fit for battle are deemed to be worth preserving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, is there anyone out there that {\i1}you{\i0} need?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister and I need each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of all, I need myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance sees no point in allowing\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}unneeded individuals to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what is this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister told me that you made it\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}without even knowing what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not something you need in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I learned how to play it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've remembered\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}something very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bevel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya says it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber, do you still not\N know our coordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Observational data is insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,More time is required.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I have a lot more to learn about this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not necessary.
